{"tid":1938360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】大陸各大傳媒賴唔到美國　　就開始發功賴意大利","createTime":"2020-03-22T13:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T13:45:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"af29b8e4f3fe1b005e111c96bf8e0bef163a0b13","tid":1938360,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎還未好，就開始發動黨媒做國際文宣，不停放假消息。中國起初想指武漢肺炎來自美國，更找到中國外交部趙立堅在Twitter發放有關消息。事發後美國白宮勁嬲，不單總統特朗普連日使用中國病毒這個稱呼，白宮官員都有類似叫法。中國政府可能發現事敗，再利用黨媒把責任推卸至意大利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/03/china-media-starts-to-blame-italy-as-the-source-of-coronavirus-wuhan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fchina-media-starts-to-blame-italy-as-the-source-of-coronavirus-wuhan%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=87969967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/03/china-media-starts-to-blame-italy-as-the-source-of-coronavirus-wuhan/</a>"},{"pid":"c582e68f8f4867d5c8e694b677ffaca894fb00ff","tid":1938360,"uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"今天中國大陸多個傳媒，以及一些被中國政府控制的英文傳媒，開始聲稱引述一位意大利研究所主任消息，指意大利於11月知道有一種奇怪的新肺炎，而且很嚴重。他們續指，這意味著在中國爆發前，病毒就已經在意大利出現。<br />\n<br />\n意大利目前確診個案過多，政府又是否有時間就此回應，暫時未清楚。"},{"pid":"aaa2ec55b28a8f44aa5cf38d9bbbc5f31532f923","tid":1938360,"uid":6058,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"今舖真係一帶一怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撩興完呢個就撩興嗰個<br />\n犯眾憎<br />\n班五毛就同義和團冇分別<br />\n睇來百國聯軍不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea429de18349cb697a0d19c7d11db4a4472bd05","tid":1938360,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"加速主義者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s